re-data registry with no external dependencies or I/O.\n\n## Quality\n**PASS.** \n- Code is well-documented with docstrings.\n- Type hints are used throughout and pass `mypy` (as verified by LEAD and confirmed by inspection).\n- Tests pass cleanly and cover edge cases (e.g., fallback logic, unknown relationship IDs).\n\n## Issues Found\n- None.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\n- Implementation is excellent. The pattern alignment with `synthesis_architecture_registry` is highly appreciated and ensures long-term maintainability.\n- No further action required for this task.\n"}}
